name: Ep. 127 - The Expanse Telltale Game w/ Special Guest Cara Gee
summary: Ty Franck (one half of James S.A. Corey) is joined by a special guest... the Cara Gee ('Drummer' on The Expanse)! Cara stopped by to talk about her new cool Expanse Telltale game and Wes even shows up as well as a one of our patrons...
